completely absent in comparison to the aromas

tected using SPME extraction. It is noteworthy that
the HS-SPME analysis, had favored a qualitative esti-
mation of the volatile components using a small
amount of plant. Finally, further works on the HS-
SPME are needed to improve the extraction efficiency
such as selection of fiber, optimization of extraction
